{"tid":842660,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"深圳海底撈火鍋驚現疑似衛生巾？ 顧客發難索償數百萬","createTime":"2018-09-30T13:39:05.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-02T10:55:57.000Z","uid":39464,"like":267,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":94,"replies":[{"pid":"d4231259d72bc35d1c389791ad96a5fc0b6f0e0d","tid":842660,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-30T13:39:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://static.stheadline.com/stheadline/inewsmedia/20180930/_2018093018472256389.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.stheadline.com%2Fstheadline%2Finewsmedia%2F20180930%2F_2018093018472256389.jpg&h=df116cf5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n有顧客在「海底撈」火鍋内發現異物，疑似衛生巾護墊。截圖<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n受港人歡迎的火鍋連鎖集團「海底撈」，近日有顧客在深圳福田區分店用餐時，發現鍋内有異物，懷疑是衛生巾護墊。經理解釋異物為墊肉的紙，但該顧客不接受，並發難要求賠償數百萬，期間更損壞部分餐具，於是職員報警。不過未能證實物品為衛生巾，所以當時餐廳願退還800多元人民幣作補償。<br />\n<br />\n事主倪小姐在深圳福田區卓越世紀廣場的海底撈剛用餐時，發現火鍋中有一塊奇怪的東西。她表示，「剛開始我以為是肉，一看不對，後面以為是紙巾，但看清楚了也不對。」<br />\n<br />\n倪小姐立即詢問經理，對方則聲稱是廚房用來墊肉的紙，並從廚房取出一包墊肉紙作為對比，表示油鍋來料全部無問題，更可以帶領倪小姐參觀後堂、工廠。倪小姐則表示「油鍋裡的東西和他拿來對比的墊肉紙根本不是同一種東西。」<br />\n<br />\n涉事海底撈分店負責人表示，客人聲稱在用餐過程中發現火鍋中有疑似衛生巾護墊的物體，客人要求退還餐費。負責人表示，畢竟在門店裡發生不滿意的事情，所以當時餐廳願退還800多元人民幣作補償。<br />\n<br />\n負責人亦表示，當時倪小姐情緒比較激動，提出賠償數百萬人民幣的要求，還損壞了一些餐具。工作人員見狀便報警請警方到場協調。警察到場後，要求倪小姐賠償門店受損餐具的金額，並查看監控錄像後沒有發現異常情況。<br />\n<br />\n倪小姐表示，要求賠償百萬元只是一怒之下說的。當時要求商家道歉時遭對方拒絕，對方更指異物是倪小姐自己帶來，故此才會要求賠償。<br />\n<br />\n店鋪已查看閉路電視，當時畫面正好背對鏡頭，負責人稱存在疑點，已將相關片段交於警方，同時未能確定異物是什麼。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.stheadline.com/stheadline/inewsmedia/20180930/_2018093018585193521.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.stheadline.com%2Fstheadline%2Finewsmedia%2F20180930%2F_2018093018585193521.jpg&h=c27ef858&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hd.stheadline.com/news/realtime/chi/1329780/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhd.stheadline.com%2Fnews%2Frealtime%2Fchi%2F1329780%2F&d=HsndlIiz%2Fi%2Fc61jSc1ST0r%2BnoHux5cIPnxEj5ZZbdh4%3D&h=f2ab9811\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhd.stheadline.com%2Fnews%2Frealtime%2Fchi%2F1329780%2F&h=8b3ddba4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://hd.stheadline.com/news/realtime/chi/1329780/</a>"},{"pid":"ff0994d93bf09d6a27f53106e0501b81b955ce2d","tid":842660,"uid":3457,"like":627,"dislike":8,"score":619,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-30T13:40:03.000Z","msg":"你是不是中國人呀！ ？<br />\n是就沒事兒吧 <br />\n有黨吧！"},{"pid":"fbc1b2aeed3b70af3b60b08f04aeee31a6a64a07","tid":842660,"uid":211074,"like":36,"dislike":13,"score":23,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-30T13:41:37.000Z","msg":"唔好話中國呀 做廚房好多都無人性<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e276002ab867e2ac78215e4863f7fdddccddddac","tid":842660,"uid":213647,"like":98,"dislike":3,"score":95,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-30T13:42:09.000Z","msg":"大驚小怪<br />\n有💩都唔出奇"},{"pid":"ad8d4abe8b78090236e98b792eba30d35e640f98","tid":842660,"uid":79182,"like":465,"dislike":2,"score":463,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-09-30T13:43:18.000Z","msg":"當護墊的確唔係咁薄 有層膠喺底<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"110a6cab9cf167bc808235922e0f0fbfa5b1fbe3","tid":842660,"uid":56453,"like":84,"dislike":1,"score":83,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-30T13:44:08.000Z","msg":"啲人最中意北上深圳食嘢<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"211e4afacb935f8499e3363730995fb7c6779c13","tid":842660,"uid":29080,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-30T13:47:54.000Z","msg":"好吃"},{"pid":"752af726b2a7a1918b6f6b8ce2f80d48ae29f38c","tid":842660,"uid":52358,"like":142,"dislike":3,"score":139,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-30T13:49:38.000Z","msg":"有得你叫海底撈<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a3560a0ed8af28b5bc8f571cc653cf8de9d7db14","tid":842660,"uid":87511,"like":321,"dislike":11,"score":310,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-09-30T13:50:02.000Z","msg":"所以你班北上消遣嘅柒頭點解會畀人話係港豬,咪就係咁解囉<br />\n<br />\n香港嘢食雖然都愈嚟愈貴,但係點都平過你北上嘅車費<br />\n仲未計啲車程時間<br />\n<br />\n而且眾所鳩知上面蘇丹紅,奶粉,頭髮豉油,坑渠油,千年雪肉...etc數都數唔哂嘅黑心食物乜撚都有<br />\n真係就連雞蛋咁撚平嘅食物,啲大陸閪都可以整隻假雞蛋出嚟呃鳩人仲賺到錢<br />\n<br />\n啲蝗蟲平時咁撚奶共都識走落嚟香港搶嘢食啦<br />\n你班港豬明知上面咁多黑心食物,都仲要走上去搶屎食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"24314741f0a18b01c615848508ce01f0f9e15e3c","tid":842660,"uid":2419,"like":38,"dislike":2,"score":36,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-30T13:56:32.000Z","msg":"痴線 大陸好撚安全架 我去親都冇事"},{"pid":"54d3b531fbdf6d5af9e3274898cce85344d6a796","tid":842660,"uid":128603,"like":11,"dislike":1,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-30T13:56:53.000Z","msg":"嘩，真係好先進。<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8fdd2190305b5c4e2bca610b0f143b23d98af75f","tid":842660,"uid":42246,"like":94,"dislike":9,"score":85,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-30T13:59:09.000Z","msg":"9成9自己放入去屈返筆<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7747bd24ea0ab3d5d0de9441b3d8628048f663cf","tid":842660,"uid":49215,"like":24,"dislike":5,"score":19,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-30T14:00:38.000Z","msg":"會唔會咁細塊"},{"pid":"65233f0ad8f92267fee303f60424375886ef051c","tid":842660,"uid":44454,"like":43,"dislike":1,"score":42,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-30T14:01:40.000Z","msg":"證明個湯底好衛生囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d76df156d3f4b2f917860c3cc44fdfd06fdbcc54","tid":842660,"uid":51639,"like":174,"dislike":1,"score":173,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-30T14:01:41.000Z","msg":"護墊撚有咁透咁薄咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5e58dcf3b927653